import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { ActivatedRoute } from '@angular/router'; import { IDeliveryType } from '../delivery-type.model'; @Component({ selector: 'jhi-delivery-type-detail', templateUrl: './delivery-type-detail.component.html', }) export class DeliveryTypeDetailComponent implements OnInit { deliveryType: IDeliveryType | null = null; constructor(protected activatedRoute: ActivatedRoute) {} ngOnInit(): void { this.activatedRoute.data.subscribe(({ deliveryType }) => { this.deliveryType = deliveryType; }); } previousState(): void { window.history.back(); } }
